          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Mn-57 decays with a half-life of 1.75 min followed by",
                " two gamma-transitions of 0.122 and 0.136 MeV. The two",
                " transitions could not be found in the gamma-spectrum,",
                " but an analysis of the decay-curve yielded a 1.8 min",
                " component.  Due to the uncertainty of the graphical",
                " separation results an upper limit of",
                " 0.017 mb +-50% for the Co-59(n,He-3) reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Absorption, selfabsorption, extension of source etc.",
                " Competetive experements with the reactions Fe56(n,p)",
                " and Fe57(n,p) which lead to the same residual nuclei",
                " as the Co59(n,He3) and the Co59(n,alpha) monitor-",
                " reaction"
              ]
            }
          ],
